      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/27/1/52/9",
      "text": [
        ": إن أصحاب موسى ابتلوا بنهر، وهو قول الله عز وجل:﴿إِنَّ اللهَ مُبْتَلِيكُمْ بِنَهَرٍ﴾ وإن أصحاب القائم يبتلون بمثل ذلك."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayyid-athar-husain-s-h-rizvi": [
          "H 491 - It is narrated from Fadhl from Abdur Rahman bin Abu Hashim from Ali bin Abu Hamza from Abu Basir from Imam Ja’far Sadiq (a.s) that he said: “The companions of Musa (a.s) were tested by the stream and it is that which the Almighty Allah has said: “Surely Allah will try you with a river…” <a href=\"/books/quran:2#h249\">[2:249]</a> The companions of Qaim (a.s) would also be tested in the same way."
        ]
      }
    },
